                        "displayName": "Saurabh Bajaj",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "Etc/UTC"
                    },
                    "body": "Try setting the environment variable ARROW_LIBHDFS_DIR to the explicit location of libhdfs.so at the worker nodes. That's what worked for me.\u00a0",
